Pattern Recognition

Sorting + Two Pointers + Duplicate Handling

Key Observation:
Fix one element.
The remaining problem becomes:
Two Sum on a sorted array.

This transforms:
O(n³)
into:
O(n²)
and is the standard interview solution for 3Sum. 
